data.description: Conveniently located near Tyndall AFB, this almost new home (built in 2023) is one to see.  A 3 bedroom and 2 bath carpet free home with LVP flooring throughout that does not have an HOA and is in an X flood zone.  It has all the touches, quartz countertops, soft close drawer and cabinets, stainless steel appliances, kitchen island, open floorplan, window blinds, partially furnished home, covered front porch, back patio, short term or long term rental option, security system paid for the year, etc.  See attached list of items that convey.  The home even comes has a current survey.  Do not hesitate to make an appointment to tour this home.
